rows.label: qst200810_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh, it seems you've finally
gathered the Healing Teak.

rows.label: qst200810_msg0102
rows.name:
Well then, I'll start
processing it right away,
so please wait a moment.

rows.label: qst200810_msg0104
rows.name:
Alright, it's done! With this,
you can support any large tree!

rows.label: qst200810_msg0106
rows.name: Is that splint really that amazing, mo?

rows.label: qst200810_msg0107
rows.name:
Yes. Even after being processed,
it's still breathing and growing.

rows.label: qst200810_msg0108
rows.name:
Yes, that's right. We never
kill trees or plants.

rows.label: qst200810_msg0109
rows.name:
We change their form and
live together with them.

rows.label: qst200810_msg0110
rows.name:
Now, hurry and go heal
that Saffronia tree!
